19,33, the calculated hole trap densities of the control and target devices were 1.06 × 1018 cm−3 and 6.69 × 1017 cm−3, respectively. These results represented good film-forming properties and reduced trap states of the target QDs, which laid a solid groundwork for constructing high-performance devices.

